<style>
  .founder { padding: 100px 0; background: var(--color-background); }
  .founder__grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center; }
  .founder__media { border-radius: var(--radius-soft); overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft); }
  
  .founder__title { font-size: 3.2rem; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .founder__subtitle { font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; }
  .founder__content { font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .founder__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .founder__title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
  }
</style>

<section class="founder animate-reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="founder__grid">
      <div class="founder__media">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544126592-807daa2b565b?q=80&w=800" alt="Meet our Founder">
      </div>
      <div class="founder__body">
        <span class="founder__subtitle">Meet our Founder</span>
        <h2 class="founder__title">A mama of five—who loves her sleep</h2>
        <p class="founder__content">It all started when our founder’s youngest daughter couldn’t sleep due to chronic eczema. She became a woman on a mission to alleviate her daughter’s discomfort. What she didn’t expect was to find the answer in a breathable, incredibly soft fabric made with sensitive skin in mind.</p>
        <a href="/pages/our-story" class="button">Read Her Story</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{ "name": "Founder Story" }
{% endschema %}
